item.title: [317] claws help!
item.dc:creator: @Mr_Bobby Mr. Bobby
item.description:
@Mr_Bobby wrote:

/Client Side/

class8.java is for adding the ints for example the rotation,inventory models etc.

Models folder is for adding the actual item model.
/End Client Side/

/Server Side/

Item.cfg is for editing item strengths.

Client.java might have the claws code special attack strengths in there.

/End Server Side/
